%^BOLD%^-=%^CYAN%^Cold Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The cold domain draws upon snow and ice to create both protection for the caster and devastating effects upon the victim.

Clerics with the Cold Domain gain the following benefits:
- Cold resistance equal to their cleric level.
- %^CYAN%^Ice Bolt%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

The cold domain contains the following spells:

Frostfield, Frost Orb, Ice Storm, Hypothermia, Avalanche 

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lord Shadow

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
